
<h1>Live sampling</h1>

<p>Giada gives you the ability to record anything coming in from your soundcard thanks to its live sampler and the master input channel. Configure your device in the <a href="{{ url('documentation/show/configuration') }}">Configuration panel</a> first, then turn up the knob of the <strong>input volume</strong> <img src="{{ url('img/docs/gui_inputmeter.png') }}" alt="The input peakmeter" title="The input peakmeter" class="inline" /> in the main window.</p>

